== 製作 ==
2019年6月，宣佈[[喬治·克隆尼|喬治·克隆尼]]將執導及主演改編自莉莉·布魯克斯-達爾頓（{{lang|en|Lily Brooks-Dalton}}）的2016年小說《永夜漂流》的電影，該片由{{le|馬克·L·史密斯|Mark L. Smith}}編劇，[[Netflix|Netflix]]發行<ref>{{cite web|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|url=https://deadline.com/2019/06/george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-mark-l-smith-movie-netflix-1202636253/|title=George Clooney To Direct & Star In Film Adaptation Of ‘Good Morning, Midnight’ Novel For Netflix|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-06-24|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108001423/https://deadline.com/2019/06/george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-mark-l-smith-movie-netflix-1202636253/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月，[[費莉絲蒂·瓊斯|費莉絲蒂·瓊斯]]加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|last2=N'Duka|first2=Amanda|url=https://deadline.com/2019/07/felicity-jones-joins-george-clooney-netflix-good-morning-midnight-1202643693/|title=Felicity Jones Joins George Clooney Netflix ‘Good Morning, Midnight’ Film Adaptation|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-07-09|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2019-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190927052407/https://deadline.com/2019/07/felicity-jones-joins-george-clooney-netflix-good-morning-midnight-1202643693/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月，[[凱爾·錢德勒|凱爾·錢德勒]]和[[大衛·奧伊羅|大衛·奧伊羅]]加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last=N'Duka|first=Amanda|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/kyle-chandler-george-clooney-felicity-jones-netflix-film-1202668123/|title=Kyle Chandler Joins George Clooney & Felicity Jones In Clooney-Helmed Post-Apocalyptic Netflix Film|publisher=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2019-08-14|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029160550/https://deadline.com/2019/08/kyle-chandler-george-clooney-felicity-jones-netflix-film-1202668123/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/david-oyelowo-george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-1203308302/|title=David Oyelowo Joins George Clooney in ‘Good Morning, Midnight’ Adaptation (EXCLUSIVE)|publisher=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2019-08-20|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108001257/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/david-oyelowo-george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-1203308302/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，{{le|蒂芙尼·布恩|Tiffany Boone}}和凱歐琳·斯普林格爾（{{lang|en|Caoilinn Springall}}）加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tiffany-boone-joins-george-clooneys-good-morning-midnight-adaptation-1245036|title=Tiffany Boone Joins George Clooney's 'Good Morning, Midnight' Adaptation|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2019-10-03|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029210917/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/tiffany-boone-joins-george-clooneys-good-morning-midnight-adaptation-1245036|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月，[[德米安·畢齊|德米安·畢齊]]加盟劇組。2020年1月，[[蘇菲·朗朵|蘇菲·朗朵]]、[[伊森·派克|伊森·派克]]、{{le|提姆·羅斯|Tim Russ}}和[[米利亞姆·肖爾|米利亞姆·肖爾]]加盟劇組<ref>{{cite web|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-adds-sophie-rundle-ethan-peck-1269306|title=George Clooney's 'Good Morning, Midnight' Adaptation Adds Ethan Peck, Sophie Rundle|publisher=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2020-01-14|accessdate=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223235028/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/george-clooney-good-morning-midnight-adds-sophie-rundle-ethan-peck-1269306|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

